@startuml
title Feature 009. Корзина и промо-предложения. Sequence

actor "Покупатель / партнер" as User
participant "Frontend web-shell" as Frontend
participant "CartController\nmodule cart" as CartController
participant "CartService\nmodule cart" as CartService
participant "CatalogService\nmodule catalog" as CatalogService
participant "PromotionPolicy\nmodule cart" as PromotionPolicy
participant "AuditService\nmodule cart" as AuditService

User -> Frontend: Открывает /cart
Frontend -> CartController: GET /api/cart/current
CartController -> CartService: getCurrentCart(user, MAIN)
CartService -> CatalogService: refreshAvailability(productCodes, campaignId, roleSegment)
CatalogService --> CartService: цены, остатки, лимиты, публикация
CartService -> PromotionPolicy: recalculate(cart, MAIN)
PromotionPolicy --> CartService: totals, offer statuses, blocking reasons
CartService --> CartController: CartResponse
CartController --> Frontend: CartResponse без hardcoded user-facing text
Frontend --> User: Строки, итоги, доступность, STR_MNEMO_* через i18n

User -> Frontend: Меняет количество строки
Frontend -> CartController: PATCH /api/cart/items/{lineId}\nIdempotency-Key
CartController -> CartService: changeQuantity(lineId, quantity, expectedVersion)
CartService -> CatalogService: validateQuantity(productCode, quantity, campaignId)
CatalogService --> CartService: maxAllowedQuantity, availability
CartService -> PromotionPolicy: recalculate(cart, MAIN)
CartService -> AuditService: ADD/CHANGE_QUANTITY audit event
CartService --> CartController: CartResponse
CartController --> Frontend: CartResponse
Frontend --> User: Обновленные итоги или причина блокировки

User -> Frontend: Открывает /cart/shopping-offers
Frontend -> CartController: GET /api/cart/shopping-offers
CartController -> CartService: getShoppingOffers(user, MAIN)
CartService -> PromotionPolicy: findApplicableOffers(cart, MAIN)
PromotionPolicy -> CatalogService: checkOfferProductsAvailability(productCodes)
CatalogService --> PromotionPolicy: availability и цены
PromotionPolicy --> CartService: ShoppingOffersResponse
CartService --> CartController: ShoppingOffersResponse
CartController --> Frontend: ShoppingOffersResponse
Frontend --> User: Наборы, подарки, cross-sell, upsell, free-delivery progress

User -> Frontend: Применяет offer
Frontend -> CartController: POST /api/cart/shopping-offers/{offerId}/apply\nIdempotency-Key
CartController -> CartService: applyOffer(offerId, MAIN)
CartService -> PromotionPolicy: validateAndApplyOffer(cart, offerId, MAIN)
PromotionPolicy -> CatalogService: validateProducts(relatedProductCodes)
CatalogService --> PromotionPolicy: доступность и ограничения
PromotionPolicy --> CartService: измененные строки и applied offer
CartService -> AuditService: APPLY_OFFER audit event
CartService --> CartController: CartResponse
CartController --> Frontend: CartResponse
Frontend --> User: Оффер применен или показана STR_MNEMO_* причина

alt Партнерский дозаказ
  User -> Frontend: Открывает /cart/supplementary
  Frontend -> CartController: GET /api/cart/supplementary/current
  CartController -> CartService: getCurrentCart(user, SUPPLEMENTARY)
  CartService -> PromotionPolicy: validateSupplementaryAccess(user, campaignId)
  PromotionPolicy --> CartService: разрешение или STR_MNEMO_SUPPLEMENTARY_ORDER_FORBIDDEN
  CartService --> CartController: CartResponse или ErrorResponse
  CartController --> Frontend: response
  Frontend --> User: Отдельная корзина дозаказа или контролируемая блокировка
end

User -> Frontend: Переходит к checkout
Frontend -> CartController: POST /api/cart/validate
CartController -> CartService: validateForCheckout(user, MAIN)
CartService -> CatalogService: validateCampaignAndAvailability(cart.lines)
CartService -> PromotionPolicy: validateBenefitsAndOffers(cart)
CartService -> AuditService: VALIDATION_FAILED audit event при блокировках
CartService --> CartController: CartValidationResponse
CartController --> Frontend: CartValidationResponse
Frontend --> User: Checkout route или список причин исправления

@enduml
